          "date": "2012-01-19 06:45:48.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-907 nfs: open only fetches OPEN lock",
        "message": "LU-907 nfs: open only fetches OPEN lock\n\nOpen only fetches OPEN lock, because open(O_READONLY) will fetch\nlock with mode LCK_CR, which doesn't make sense for LOOKUP or\nUPDATE lock; and this can avoid open conflict with setattr/getattr.\nIn this way open lock cache is really effective for nfs export.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <laisiyao@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I9b91dad235d3df2ea9182daea8add23874e08df8\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
